Bitcoin Last 6 months Liquidity. FTX issue triggered the fall of price to grab the liquidity.

Following the collapse of FTX, #Bitcoin investors have been withdrawing coins to self-custody at a historic rate of 106k $BTC/month.This compares with only three other times:- Apr 2020- Nov 2020- June-July 2022

In direct response to the failure of FTX, #Bitcoin investors, of all wallet cohorts, have made a distinct behavioural shift towards self-custody.From Shrimp, to Whales, #Bitcoin on-chain balances are on the rise.
There should be the bear for #Bitcoin till end of the year. The winter is still.
